    <h1 class="subheader">Tom Perez: Liar, Extremist, Ethically Challenged</h1>
    <p id="entry-details">
        
        <a class="content-tag" href="/topic/elections-elections-dnc/">
            <strong>DNC</strong>
        </a>
        - December 14, 2016
    </p>
</div>


